Public Methods

public boolean equals (Object other)

public String getDescription ()

Returns an HTML string that is a description of this feature. This can be null if no description can be found, or if the description has not yet been found.

public String getGmeFeatureId ()

Returns the Google Maps Engine feature ID for this feature. This can be null if no GME feature ID can be found, or if the ID has not yet been found.

public MapsEngineLayer getLayer ()

Returns the MapsEngineLayer in which the feature is contained.

public LatLng getPoint ()

Returns the point of the feature closest to the tap.
